Trade/Device Name(s): LifeOutcomes C-Quest™ Blood Culture Sampling Device
Document Summary: FDA 510(k) summary for LifeOutcomes C-Quest Blood Culture Sampling Device, designed to reduce blood culture contamination through initial specimen diversion.
Indications for Use Summary: Intended to collect patient blood samples and sequester the first portion to reduce blood culture contamination, used with scalp vein sets for venipuncture or IV extension sets, compatible with blood culture tubes or standard syringes.
